	<title component="not-workbook">Solving exponential equations (and logs)</title>
	<title component="workbook">Solving exponential equations (and logs) - Practice exercises</title>
	<introduction component="not-workbook">

		<p>
			In order to use the <xref ref="assemblage-shoes-and-socks" text="title" />, we need to know the opposites of the operations that we use to evaluate functions. So far, we have a pretty good library of operations and their opposites:
